Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry for inconveniencing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now.\NIt's what any proper person would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...\NI didn't mean to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so terribly sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Main thing is that\NI'm glad to see you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NBut it was all due to my carelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much, sir.\NI'm glad you were kind enough to step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyo,\Nlet's get out of the sun for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll leave you to your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo, are you sure\Nthat you're feeling alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry if I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take\Nbetter care of yourself, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miyo, you need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,no idea just how special you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 9\NDROWNING IN DREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she\Npush herself that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So there were remnants of a gift-user
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were only there\Nduring her nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How feasible does it sound\Nto use a supernatural ability
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from a remote location?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an Usuba could do\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But there should've been a crack\Nin the barrier if that had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely to have been\Noutside interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is speculation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but the mounting evidence supports\Nmy theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's connected\Nto her Usuba heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo is an Usuba? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a strong case for it,\Nwith a handful of clues to go off of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A wedding for a Sumi Usuba\Nmarrying into the Saimori house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it just feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've thought\Nshe could be one of the Usuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Miyo wasn't born with the gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,hypothetically,\Nif the Usuba family blood is in her veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance her body could be having\Nsome kind of adverse reaction to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it be a problem now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it was the only\Nother possibility I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she know anything\Nabout the Usuba family gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo lost her mother.\NShe was too young to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt she's even aware\Nof her Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I asked directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,she may not want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been guarding her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to hide her feelings\Nmore than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she just doesn't\Nwant us to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wish\Nshe'd give us the option to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You catch sight of a bear in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A civilian attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We think it was a Grave Grotesquerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Godo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the woods\Nnear the Forbidden Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They found a man in a rough way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, he's unconscious\Nin a comatose state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on symptoms he's showing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Grave's condition,\Nit looks like Grotesqueries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already reached\Nthe populated area this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our predictions\Nfor their movement were way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ministry of the Imperial House\Ncan't manage this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore they infiltrate the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate this...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why won't these nightmares ever stop?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They keep playing over and over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm far from refined like Miss Hazuki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I'm sliding backward.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She significantly decreased\Nmy study hours since I collapsed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm wasting the perfect opportunity\Nto learn from her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry,\NI'll be working tonight too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll prepare you a lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can deliver it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's all right.\NYou should take it easy and rest.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How are you feeling?\NAre you sure you're doing okay?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm perfectly fine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't feel the need\Nto worry about me. It's all right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh, sorry, Godo just called for me.\NI have to go.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I hope everything at work goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what we've seen, it looks like\Nthey're heading straight for the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll descend like a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we heard anything\Nfrom the Ministry yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still trying to get them to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're slow to decide\Nand aren't measuring up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll establish\Na perimeter around the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Request urgent permission to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna sweep it\Nin one fell swoop, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go reach out to the Ministry\Nas soon as we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For now,\Nprepare for deployment, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The imperial capital will be\Nunder our unit's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I had every intention of coming in\Nand making the food for us today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I went to the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything was already prepared,\Nready and hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of work\Nwhen you aren't fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm feeling\Nmuch better now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't worry about that and enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm! It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooking is one of Miss Miyo's many skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so very talented\Nwith all that she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make a tasty dish like this\Nto save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it.\NI'm actually a terrible cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at girls' school,\Nmy grades in cooking class were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I would burn whatever I grilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and things were too salty, too spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even holding a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My only skill was cutting my finger\Nand not noticing what I'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that made for such a challenge\Nwhenever you got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you not to drag up the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly regret\Nhow all of that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by far the biggest regret\Nthat I have in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret the way my marriage ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got married\Npretty quickly, at only 17.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I was born\Nas the daughter of the Kudos,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was prepared for a political marriage.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my husband was a kind and good man.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was truly happy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't get along\Nwith his family very well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Basic chores were not my strong suit,\Nand I was immature at the time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was pretty far off\Nfrom their version of an ideal wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My husband would normally comfort me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there was one time{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where we both got emotional\Nwhile talking things out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After a big fight, we decided to divorce.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But after that, I went to\Nmy parents' house and cooled down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got hit with a wave of regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of things to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,\NI felt as though I had lost so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe... I haven't tried\Nas hard as I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you regret\Nthe most in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the things\Nthat you're not good at,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't run away\Nor make excuses for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand up and face them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hope from now on\Nthat you can prioritize how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take that time,\Nthen you can avoid having regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- like mine.\N- Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about what it is\Nyou want for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your version of an ideal life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not really sure\Nhow to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I want...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to become a wife\Nthat would be a good fit for Lord Kudo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be like Miss Hazuki\Nby becoming a refined lady.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I was someone like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine. I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It had never crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never tried to picture\Nwhat an ideal life could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is one thing\Nthat I'm certain of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right by Lord Kudo's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the way you talk about him\Nwhen he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one lucky man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Took more leg work than you could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Found every Sumi in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Sumi Usuba is one of them,\Nthen it's well worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, it's great that we got it\Nnarrowed down to women named Sumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no way of telling\Nwhich one is the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our only lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only hope we have\Nof reaching out to the Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any information is better than none.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right\Nif I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miyo.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that work's been so busy\Nthat we haven't had time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Your work is very important.\NI don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are you sure\Nthat there's nothing bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what is... What's Miss Hazuki like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do her mannerisms change\Nwhen she talks to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I suppose you and I haven't\Nreally talked about many personal things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right\Nif I asked you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I,\Nour relationship has never been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're already aware\Nof how loud she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which gets on my nerves\Nevery now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's less about "like" or "dislike".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kind of feelings don't really apply\Nto our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We grew up\Nin the same environment together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so we always know\Nwhat the other is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't speak with restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our personalities may not align,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think as she is,\Nshe's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Does any of that answer your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a wonderful person\Nto have grown up with!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't had\Nsomeone like that in my life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...why don't you sit a little closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sit? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're feeling lonely, then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in pain, then say that it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't know what you're feeling\Nif you don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling lonely though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't? Because I feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that you aren't lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say that from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to tell me\Nhow you really feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,know that I'm going to be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that it's selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me anything.\NI'll listen to all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel guilty for seeking comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're family now, are we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of that is supporting each other\Nthrough thick and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo is very kind.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}But still...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I really want to become Mrs. Kudo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I can't use him as a crutch.\NI must be strong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These are my problems.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can't handle them on my own,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how could I ever support a whole family?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the man who...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. It's lovely to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure how things had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, you've recovered\Nsince that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been a shock.\NThank you so much for being there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come now.\NNo need to thank me for any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I was here to see a Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. He's actually at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that he was off duty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very busy at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that he was called in\Nat the last minute and had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize I didn't call in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata Tsuruki is my name. Pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I'm Miyo Saimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, I know.\NI'm quite well aware of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the talk\Nof the social scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A rumor that had everyone's ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The infamous Mr. Kudo has finally\Nfound himself a suitable fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I suppose the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of his "frozen tundra" personality\Nwere right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that you appear\Nto be absolutely exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I noticed it in town.\NThis is the result of neglect, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it is unacceptable to force you\Nto work to the point of fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... None of what happened is\NLord Kudo's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you push yourself\Nuntil you collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If he understood your true worth,\Nhe wouldn't do this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurd! As if you aren't a lady already,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting you to learn\Nthe proper ways to behave,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,yet offering nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would this be so important
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd force a person\Ninto this educational gauntlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one\Nwho wanted to learn all of these at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo is only cooperating\Nafter I begged him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say such awful things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.\NWhat I've said to you is out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I should as well. I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My attitude has been extremely rude today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been forthright\Nfrom the start. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an offer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A unique role\Nthat only you could ever fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to reach out at any time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if the interest strikes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL ADVISOR\NARATA TSURUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A role that only I could ever fill?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's late, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's Ministry staff or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's disrespectful to have you\Nwaiting on him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can proceed with our preparations\Nfor the operation regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty tired there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't concern yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After things are handled here,\NI plan to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Miss Miyo.\NYou should go home for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission was granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Authority will now be transferred\Nto Commander Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are free to act as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. We will start\Nthe large-scale sweep operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get this under control quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or further damage could strike\Nthe capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! I can't say\Nhow sorry I am for being late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The impression was that you were off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistakenly ended up\Nat your home while trying to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had the pleasure of getting\Nto meet your fiancée, Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thoughtful\Nand well-mannered greeting I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be brimming\Nwith affection for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I find myself with less admiration\Nfor how you treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice that\Nshe's starting to look frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her health wastes away\Na little more each day, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She and I have crossed paths\Non a previous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She nearly collapsed on the street\Nwhen she was in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and thankfully, I was nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Na single thing about her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Miss Miyo so inconsequential\Nthat she's invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you don't even care, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you weren't there for her\Nwhen she needed you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is more than enough proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You don't like small talk, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you face any difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,please feel free to contact me\Nat a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's anything\Nthat I could assist you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is strange, boss.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Out of all the Sumis\NI've come across thus far,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's only one\Nwho doesn't have a birth certificate,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they're not registered to a household.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The name is "Sumi Tsuruki."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL ADVISOR\NARATA TSURUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuruki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told her to rest, but she's...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Oh, you're home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, welcome back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I wasn't at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I should have greeted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo! Miyo, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you get so thin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you not tell me\Nthat you collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but I was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\NI don't know about the nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing you suffer\Nthrough them every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talk to me, you can lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after all this time, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really so untrustworthy\Nthat you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I didn't want to bother you\Nif it was something I could handle alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You've spent all this extra time working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I didn't want to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It seemed like you were already\Nso busy and tired, I just couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How am I the one who seems too tired
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}when you can't even tell when I get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If this is how it was going to end up,\NI never should've even given you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the opportunity to study\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, that was cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wasn't... I didn't mean...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never meant to talk to her like this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be here with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did the worst thing\NI ever could've done to her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that was the same kind of treatment\Nas the Saimoris.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm awful! That man was completely right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL ADVISOR\NARATA TSURUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsuruki is going\Nto tell me everything.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it. I have to end this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do whatever it takes\Nto end her suffering!{\i}
